headline: A Bull Market Is Here: 2 Supercharged Stocks Down More Than 20% to Buy Right Now
summary: This bull market has been running rampant for more than two years, but it's an unusual one.  While the bullish trend has been having a broad impact on the stock market, some stocks can be expected to benefit more than others as the investor-friendly run continues.  Anders Bylund (Criteo): One of the most game-changing aspects of this bull market is the ongoing return to normal consumer spending behavior.
